parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "Snakemake",
  "details": {
    "resource_manager": "SLURM",
    "singularity": "Enabled if singularity_within_snakemake is set to 1",
    "configuration_file": "conf/pipeline.yaml",
    "cluster_configuration_file": "conf/cluster.yaml",
    "dataverse": "Either harvard or demo",
    "token": "Either HARVARD_DATAVERSE_TOKEN or DEMO_DATAVERSE_TOKEN",
    "upload": "Enabled if upload is set to 1",
    "job_options": "--rerun-incomplete --nolock --use-singularity",
    "slurm_options": {
      "ntasks": "{cluster.ntasks}",
      "N": "{cluster.N}",
      "t": "{cluster.t}",
      "cpus_per_task": "{cluster.cpus_per_task}",
      "p": "{cluster.p}",
      "mem": "{cluster.mem}",
      "output": "{cluster.output}",
      "error": "{cluster.error}",
      "mail_type": "{cluster.mail_type}"
    },
    "parallelism": "12 jobs"
  }
}
```
